#1033 Mumble leaks DNS when using a proxy

You can test the SOCKS5 proxy settings by using Mumble with Tor. https:/torproject.org.
Set the proxy network to 127.0.0.1 and the port to 9050.

#1033 Mumble leaks DNS when using a proxy

This issue also occurs when using an HTTP proxy.
